{
  "stem": "20088.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we demonstrated that when my parents had a party, or a few people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We said we were going to come in and he was going to show that after a few minutes, I was going to burst out into tears.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And what I had to imagine was that we were playing, and he was going to die.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then I was so upset about it that I burst into tears.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we came in and he looked at me, and I had to imagine it, that he was going to die.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then after a few minutes, I really burst into tears, and I just couldn't stop.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And nobody knew how he managed to do this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But-- so we were always a team.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we slept together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he had a-- a torch which had white, red, and green light.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You had to filter over it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And at night, he used to tell me ghost stories, and stories about in-- red Indians, and-- and we saw slides shining on the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he made designs with his fingers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was very artistic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And you know, we were a real very happy family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then my grandparents-- my mother's parents-- lived in walking distance from where we were, and practically every second day we saw each other.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I went to sleep there a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then we had-- my mother had a sister, and my father had a sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they both had children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So those were our cousins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "My cousin from my father's sister, she was exactly my age, Gaby.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we were great friends as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And so we always went to play together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And my birthday was in May, and weather was good in May always in Austria, in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
